title: Rand Paul's neighbor pleads guilty to attacking senator
text:
Rand Paul's neighbor pleads guilty to attacking senator 10:42am EST - 01:02 
U.S. Senator Rand Paul's neighbor pleaded guilty on Friday to attacking the congressman after he became angry over a lawn care issue. Linda So reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
